	<texsetting wysiwyg="0"/><paper pagenumber="1" margin="20,20,20,25">A4</paper></head>
	
<body fontsize="12pt" fontface="ＭＳ Ｐ明朝">
<p>既に学んだように、確率密度関数<mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>が与えられたとき、<mblock><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">X</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">Y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">in</munit><munit italic="1">D</munit></mblock>となる確率は</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">P</munit><munit>(</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">X</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">Y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">in</munit><munit italic="1">D</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">D</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit></mblock></p>
<p>で与えられる。仮に確率変数<mblock><munit italic="1">X</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">Y</munit></mblock>が</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">X</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">U</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">V</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>、<mblock><munit italic="1">Y</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">psi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">U</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">V</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>と別の確率変数<mblock><munit italic="1">U</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">V</munit></mblock>で表されるとき、<mblock><munit italic="1">U</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">V</munit></mblock>の従う確率密度関数はどのようなものになるだろうか。</p>
<p>そもそも2変量の確率密度関数の重積分<mblock><munit entity="1" style="big">int</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">D</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit></mblock>は</p>
<p/>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">in</munit><munit italic="1">D</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">Delta<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>において全ての<mblock><munit entity="1">Delta<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>が0に近づくときの極限である。<mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>は<mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">psi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>と</p>
<p>簡単に<mblock><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit></mblock>の関数として表すことができる。以下、<mblock><munit entity="1">Delta<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>が<mblock><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit></mblock>によってどのように表現されるかを考察していこう。</p>
<p/>
<p/>
<p/></body></InftyDocument>
